    "They freeze when they have to start a task and say they dont know where to begin.",
    "My kid is bright, but planning and follow-through just dont happen without me.",
    "Every week feels like starting over; routines never stick.",
    "I dont want tutoring. I want a system so my student can manage school independently.",
    "Teachers say 'needs to be more responsible' but no one is teaching the skills."
  ],
