    "hero_scene": "Format: video-thumbnail hero with centered play button overlay. Scene: top-down/3-4 angle of a clean, modern desk in soft natural light. Key props: (1) one-page 'Weekly Reset' worksheet (simple boxes/lines, readable as a planning sheet but NOT filled with tiny text), (2) a laptop slightly angled showing a generic school portal/dashboard layout (use abstract UI blocks, not real brand portals; no tiny readable text), (3) a minimal checklist card and a pen/highlighter. Optional adult hands/forearms (no faces) to reinforce parent/guardian focus. Color grade: cool-neutral with primary teal accents (folder, notebook spine, subtle overlay). Composition: keep worksheet + laptop centered within the middle 70% safe area on both axes. Add the play button overlay: centered circle with subtle shadow; circle fill can be white at ~85–92% opacity; white triangle centered, slightly smaller than typical; button diameter ~18% of hero width. Deliver as PNG 1600x900.",
